# Risk tiers (0-3)


Tier 0: drafting, triage, docs — no approvals
  Gates: none

Tier 1: scoped code changes — human merge review required
  Gates: merge

Tier 2: auth, schemas, deps, data contracts, perf-critical paths — pre-approval + DQ/perf/security gates
  Gates: architecture, data, security, performance, merge

Tier 3: production actions, releases, data mutation — dual approvals + release workflow + post-check
  Gates: architecture, data, security, performance, release, merge


Stop and request approval if:
- schema or contract changes
- auth/permissions changes
- infra changes
- production actions

Current project default tier: 1
